      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were assembled from production-representative hardware lots. CMM inspection of each construct confirmed all critical dimensions within drawing tolerances. Samples span two laboratory sites to capture inter-lab variability. Required level 3 achieved."
