      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 (5° offset, 10 mm rod segment). Only one test condition was evaluated; multi-angle or multi-segment configurations were not included in this validation campaign. This factor does not meet the required level 3, representing a known gap in the validation scope. Required level 3; achieved level 2."
