      "rationale": "CAD geometry for each of the 11 constructs was updated using CMM-measured dimensions. Friction coefficients were determined from dedicated pin-on-disk tribology tests on the same surface finish. Boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry within 0.1 mm. Equivalency documented in simulation-test comparison report REP-2026-003. Required level 3 achieved."
